text: - The AWS Executive Briefing Center

offers AWS customers and
partners an opportunity
to experience Amazon's unique culture.

Learn about the latest
advances in AWS technologies

and discover Amazon's
leadership principles firsthand.
We'll work backward,

starting with your priorities,
challenges, and goals,

to frame the day around what's
important to your business.
Collaborate with AWS executives.
Build with innovators

and discover insights from
industry leading experts.
We'll keep your objectives top of mind,

focusing on establishing
innovative solutions
to accomplish your desired outcomes.
Dive into specific goals,
interact with AWS technology,
and learn about products and solutions

that can power your
organization's transformation.

Immerse yourself in
Amazon's peculiar culture
to inspire elevated thinking
and create revolutionary change.

Let's explore what we
can achieve together.
